rehydrate porcini, retain liquid
saute garlic and shallots
finely chop mushrooms and porcini, add to pan and saute until dark brown. 
add dried rosemary and thyme towards end
deglaze with wine and porcini liquid, simmer until reduced, season
pulse in blender with parsley
add finely chopped goats cheese and mix
cool in fridge for 1hr

make ravioli and cook

mix butter and grated truffle, mix
toast some pine nuts
melt and slightly brown butter. Toss ravioli in butter
Serve, dressed with pine nuts and rocket
